## Error Reference

### XBRL 2.1 Core Errors

| Code | Meaning | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `xbrl.5.2.4.2` | Fact contextRef references undeclared context | Declare context element before any fact referencing it |
| `xbrl.5.2.5.2` | Fact unitRef references undeclared unit | Declare unit element before the fact |
| `xbrl.5.2.6.2` | Numeric fact missing decimals or precision | Add `decimals="-6"` to all monetary and numeric facts |
| `xbrl.5.2.2.2.3` | Period type mismatch (instant vs duration) | Match context type to element's xbrli:periodType in schema |
| `xbrl.4.6.6` | Calculation inconsistency: sum of weighted children != parent | Verify weights (+1/-1) and that all children are reported |
| `xbrl.5.2.1.1` | Duplicate facts (same element + context + unit reported twice) | Remove duplicate; if intentional use a different context |
| `xbrl.4.3` | QName prefix undeclared in namespace map | Add missing xmlns:prefix declaration to instance root |
| `xbrl.5.1.1` | Schema import missing or URL unresolvable | Verify schemaLocation URL; check DTS cache |

### SEC EFM Errors (EDGAR-Specific)

| Code | Meaning | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `EFM.6.5.20` | dei:EntityRegistrantName missing or blank | Always include complete DEI entity block |
| `EFM.6.5.21` | dei:DocumentPeriodEndDate missing | Required for all 10-K/10-Q filings |
| `EFM.6.5.35` | Monetary fact uses non-ISO 4217 unit | Use iso4217:USD, not utr:USD or plain 'USD' |
| `EFM.6.7.31` | Extension element duplicates a us-gaap element | Use the existing us-gaap element; extension only for truly custom items |
| `EFM.6.7.7`  | Presentation linkbase missing required statement | All four primary statements required in presentation linkbase |
| `EFM.6.9.5`  | iXBRL ix:nonFraction missing format attribute | Add `format="ixt:num-dot-decimal"` to all monetary inline tags |
| `EFM.6.3.4`  | Accession number format incorrect | Format: XXXXXXXXXX-YY-ZZZZZZ (10-digit CIK + 2-digit year + 6-digit seq) |

### Common iXBRL Issues

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `ixbrl:missingContext` | contextRef in ix: tag not in ix:header | Add missing context to ix:resources block |
| `ixbrl:invalidFormat` | format= value not in ixt registry | Use only approved ixt: or ixt-sec: format strings |
| EDGAR viewer shows blank statement | R-files missing or FilingSummary.xml wrong | Regenerate R-files via Arelle --plugins iXBRLViewerPlugin |
| Tagged value != XBRL value | Display text and raw value mismatch after transformation | Verify ixt: format correctly transforms display_text -> raw value |
| Orphaned contexts | Contexts declared in ix:header with no tagged facts | Remove unused contexts or add missing facts |

