## Validation & QA

### Instance Document

- [ ] All `contextRef` values declared as `<xbrli:context>` before any fact
- [ ] All `unitRef` values declared as `<xbrli:unit>` before any fact
- [ ] Every numeric fact has `decimals` attribute (not `precision` — deprecated)
- [ ] decimals consistent per statement: -6 (millions), -3 (thousands), 0 (exact)
- [ ] Period type matches element definition: instant facts use instant contexts
- [ ] All namespace prefixes declared in root element `xmlns:` map
- [ ] No duplicate facts: same element + context + unit reported once only
- [ ] All required DEI elements present (EntityRegistrantName, CIK, DocumentPeriodEndDate, DocumentType)
- [ ] Arelle validation exits with zero errors and zero EFM errors
- [ ] Calculation check: zero inconsistencies for all four primary statements

### Extension Taxonomy

- [ ] Extension namespace unique and period-dated (e.g., `http://company.com/20241231`)
- [ ] No extension elements that duplicate existing us-gaap/dei elements
- [ ] All monetary extension elements have `balance` attribute (debit or credit)
- [ ] All extension elements have labels in label linkbase (standard + totalLabel)
- [ ] Extension schema lists all four linkbase hrefs in annotation/appinfo
- [ ] Custom elements appear in calculation, presentation, and definition linkbases
- [ ] Extension schema imports us-gaap-2024 and dei-2024 base taxonomies

### iXBRL

- [ ] All `ix:nonFraction` tags have `format` attribute from approved ixt registry
- [ ] All `contextRef` values in ix: tags declared in `ix:header/ix:resources`
- [ ] No orphaned contexts (contexts declared but referenced by zero facts)
- [ ] `ix:header` contains `ix:references/link:schemaRef` pointing to company XSD
- [ ] Negative values use `sign="-"` — not a minus sign in display_text
- [ ] Hidden block contains all string DEI facts (EntityRegistrantName, etc.)
- [ ] EDGAR viewer renders all four primary statements without blank rows

### EDGAR Filing Package

- [ ] `FilingSummary.xml` present and lists every R-file
- [ ] All four linkbases present: `_cal.xml`, `_def.xml`, `_lab.xml`, `_pre.xml`
- [ ] Primary document tagged with correct form type in DEI section
- [ ] ZIP package total size within EDGAR limits (< 200 MB)
- [ ] Pre-submission check via EDGAR EFTS: https://efts.sec.gov/LATEST/search-index
- [ ] EDGAR Inline XBRL Viewer renders correctly before submission

